      "rationale": "All bench experiments conducted at 22°C ± 0.5°C and 101.3 kPa. Flow rate set by calibrated Coriolis meter (±0.3% FS). Rotational speed controlled by servo drive (±1 RPM). Conditions matched CFD inlet/outlet boundary conditions within stated uncertainty. Environmental parameters were fixed at single laboratory values; no variation across temperature, pressure, or electromagnetic environment was explored. This constitutes the targeted gap: real deployment spans 18–26°C, reduced ambient pressures up to 2500 m, and EM interference levels not present in the shielded test cell."
