      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood-pump CFD. Hemolysis power-law model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) with Heuser-Opitz constants used as per FDA guidance. Model form uncertainty acknowledged; sensitivity to turbulence model assessed via k-epsilon comparison (< 6% difference in RH). Required level 2 achieved."
